    <item>
      <title>苏伊士签署价值超过 10 亿英镑的英国废物处理协议，作为全球举措的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/suez-signs-manchester-uk-waste-deal-worth-over-1-billion-as-part-of-global-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏伊士公司延长了在英国曼彻斯特地区的废物回收合同，该合同价值超过 10 亿英镑（13 亿美元），这家法国公司正寻求扩大其全球业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/suez-signs-manchester-uk-waste-deal-worth-over-1-billion-as-part-of-global-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 09:21:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国抵押贷款批准量稳定 房地产市场保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/uk-mortgage-approvals-steady-in-sign-of-stable-housing-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国抵押贷款批准数量稳定在一年半以来的最高水平，这再次表明尽管利率处于 16 年来的最高水平，但房地产市场正在趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/uk-mortgage-approvals-steady-in-sign-of-stable-housing-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 08:44:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财报季显示美国股市走强：贝莱德</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-29/earnings-season-shows-us-equities-strength-blackrock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德的李伟表示，财报季凸显了美国股市的强劲表现，“尤其是相对于欧洲股市而言”。她在彭博电视台发表讲话时补充说，即使最新的美国 GDP 数据表明消费者活动正在降温，但这也被人工智能设备支出的增加所抵消。李伟表示：“随着消费者的疫情缓冲耗尽，消费者正在将接力棒交给人工智能支出。”（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-29/earnings-season-shows-us-equities-strength-blackrock</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 08:44:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>喜力在中国市场遭遇 9.49 亿美元损失，前景谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/heineken-takes-nearly-1b-one-off-china-charge-narrows-guidance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国这一关键市场以及美国和欧洲的消费支出面临压力，喜力啤酒公司 (Heineken NV) 对其在中国最大啤酒制造商的股份承担了 8.74 亿欧元（9.49 亿美元）的减值损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/heineken-takes-nearly-1b-one-off-china-charge-narrows-guidance</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 05:23:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚允许货币贬值以获得国际货币基金组织的救助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/ethiopia-frees-its-currency-to-attract-investors-spur-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚央行允许该国货币自由交易，这是确保获得超过 100 亿美元资金和债务减免所需的一项关键改革，该国一直在与国际货币基金组织进行谈判。比尔暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/ethiopia-frees-its-currency-to-attract-investors-spur-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 05:12:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求担忧抵消中东风险，油价接近六周低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-29</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于积极的中国经济数据和中东局势再度紧张，以及对全球需求的疑虑，油价交易价格接近六周低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-29</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 23:31:28 GMT</pubDate>
